GLP at A Glance































Leading provider of modern logistics facilities in China, Japan, US and Brazil
                                                                                                                        



US$41 billion property portfolio comprising 55 million sqm (592 million sq ft) 
                                                                                                                        



2,642 completed properties across 117 cities 




Domestic demand is a key driver of demand for GLP
                                                                                                                        



Listed on the Mainboard of Singapore Exchange Securities Trading Limited on October 18, 2010
                                                                                                                        



Nine-time winner of the Euromoney Real Estate Awards from 2007 to 2015
                                                                                                                        



    
                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                *Includes completed properties, properties under development or being repositioned and land held for future development but excludes land reserve as of 31 March 2017.
                                                                                                            


























 





